snippet.title: Jawan: Not Ramaiya Vastavaiya | Shah Rukh Khan | Atlee | Anirudh | Nayanthara | Vishal D | Shilpa R
snippet.description:
Get ready to groove like never before as "Not Ramaiya Vastavaiya", the latest dance track from the highly-anticipated Atlee directorial, Jawan, is out now. The film stars Shah Rukh Khan, Vijay Sethupathi, Nayanthara, and Deepika Padukone (in a special appearance) and is set to release in cinemas on September 7, 2023, in Hindi, Tamil, and Telugu!

#NotRamaiyaVastavaiya out now!

♪Full Song Available on♪ 
JioSaavn: https://bit.ly/3srnLI5
Spotify: https://bit.ly/3ssmbG1
Hungama: https://bit.ly/3OW4upT
Apple Music: https://bit.ly/3OYPyau
Amazon Prime Music: https://bit.ly/44vEozG
Wynk: https://bit.ly/3L0roLy
Resso: https://bit.ly/47UA7Zy
YouTube Music: https://bit.ly/3OWNbov

Music Credits:
Language - Hindi
Song Title - Not Ramaiya Vastavaiya 
Album / Movie - Jawan
Composed by Anirudh Ravichander
Lyrics - Kumaar
Vocals - Anirudh Ravichander, Vishal Dadlani & Shilpa Rao
Choreographer - Vaibhavi Merchant 

Composed, Arranged & Programmed by Anirudh Ravichander
Keyboard, Synth & Rhythm Programmed by Anirudh Ravichander
Whistle - Satish Raghunathan
Tabla - MT Aditya
Additional Rhythm Programmed by Shashank Vijay
Additional Keyboard Programmed by Arish-Pradeep PJ

Music Advisor - Ananthakrrishnan
Creative Consultant - Sajith Satya
Music Editor - Harish Ram L H
Recorded at Albuquerque Records, Chennai. Engineered by Srinivasan M, Shivakiran S, Rajesh Kannan, Jishnu Vijayan
YRF Studios, Mumbai, Engineered by Vijay Dayal & Chinmay
Mixed by Vinay Sridhar & Srinivasan M at Albuquerque Records, Chennai
Mastered by Luca Pretolesi at Studio DMI, Las Vegas Assisted by Alistair Pintus 
Music Coordinator - Velavan B

Lyrics:

Dance with me now I can’t break away
Aaj sari fikreiin tu shake away
Shake away
Dil thirakta dance wale groove pe
Nachun mai to step mera vekh ve

Vekh ve
Aaj sare kaam kal pe talke
Tak dhina dhin nache jayein taal pe
Disko jaz blues sare bhoolke
Desi wale geet pe tu jhoolke
Pehle kiya chaiya chaiya re
Ab kar tha tha thaiyya
Ramiya vasta vaiya..!
Antra

Sama mazedar hua houle houle
Thoda nashedar hua
Man ye dole
Aaj koi nachta hua sa jadu
Sar pe swar hua
Dil ye bole
Doobi khushiyon mein
Raat apni jabse suraj dhala
Chodh sharmana aaj nachle pair chakkle zara

Pahle kiya chaiya chaiiya re
Ab kar tata thaiya
Ramiya vasta vaiyaa..!


___________________________________

snippet.description:
"મારા વિરા"...તમારી સમક્ષ રજૂ કરીએ છીએ રાકેશ બારોટ અને રજલ બારોટ નું નવું ગુજરાતી રક્ષા બંધન ગીત. ભાઈ અને બહેનની ભાવનાત્મક વાર્તા 💓! માત્ર  @SaregamaGujarati પર

Listen to the best of Rakesh Barot songs only on Saregama Gujarati !
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLUzteH3czVO5WMxyPrP2RWK4MMHuCKLwL

Title : Mara Veera
Singer : Rakesh Barot, Rajal Barot
Producer : Red Velvet Cinema 
Artist : Rakesh Barot, Rajal Barot
Co Aartist : Durva Barot 
Kunj Barot.nishit Nayak
Music :ravi & Rahul
Lyrice : Chandu Raval
Dop : Dhruv Bhatiya
Editing : Montu Rajput .dhruv Bhatiya
Director - Vishnu Thakor (Adalaj)
Production : Amar Panchal, Manthan Panchal.mehul
Makeup  : Hashmukh Limabachiya.
Hair : Gayatree
Technical Support: Jenish Talaviya 
Sport Boy : Shailesh.
Light : Jitubhai.kiran
Floor Music Avenger : Sunil Kachhiya

Lyrics:
હું બેની મારી નારે ભીંજાવશો આંખડી રે......... આંખડી રે....... આંખડી રે
બેની મારી પારકી.... બેની મારી પારકી રે
યે બેની મારી નારે ભીંજાવશો આંખડી રે....
હરખ આયો વીરા તને બાંધતા રાખડી રે
હે ઓહુ તારા..... ઓહુ તારા.....ઓહું તારા....
કાળજા ના કટકા કરે ચાર ઓહું તારા (૨)
બેની મારી નારે ભીંજાવશો આંખડી રે
હો મને હરખ થયો વીરા તને બાંધતા રાખડી રે

હું તારા વિના વીરા કોણ હતું મારે મારા કારણે યે ભઈલા દુઃખ વેઠયું ભારે 
એ મારી ઉંમર બેની તને લાગી જાય દુઃખનો વાયરો તને કોઈ દાડે ના વાય (૨)
હો વીરા તું તો મારા જીવતરની લાકડી રે.... લાકડી રે..... લાકડી રે

હે બેની તું તો મારા આંગડિયા નું ફૂલ (૨)
બેની મારી નારે ભીંજાવશો આંખડી રે
આહુડા તારા કાળજા ના કટકા કરે ચાર (૨)
બેની મારી નારી ભીજવશો આ ખડી રે
હું મને હરખ આયો વીરા તને બાંધતા રાખડી રે

હું અમે પારેવડે કાલે ઉડી જાશું
તમારો ઋણ ભઈલા ચમ કરી ચૂકવશું
હો માયા લાગેલી તારી કદી ના ભુલાશે
મારું તો ઠીક ઘરની દીવાલો પણ રડશે
હું ભઈલા જેને ભય નથી તેને કાળી રાતડી રે.... રાતડી રે

મારી લાડકી રી બેની તારા વિના કરશું કોને લાડ (૨)
એની મારી નારી ભીંજાવશો આખડી રે
આહુડા તારા કાળજા ના કટકા ચાર (૨)
બેની મારી નારી ભીંજાવશો આંખડી રે
હું આમ હરખ આયો વીરા તને બાંધતા રાખડી રે મારી લાડકી બેની મારી ભીજાવશો આંખડી રે........

snippet.title: FRUIT JELLY CAKE | Colorful Healthy Fruit Jelly Cake Recipe Making in Village | Agar Agar Jelly
snippet.description:
Today, in our village, we make colorful fruit jelly using marine algae. We use healthy fruits such as Kiwi, Muskmelon Fruit, Grapes, Green, Grapes, Pomegranate, Mango, Strawberry, Papaya, White Dragon Fruit, Red Dragon Fruit, and Watermelon.

We cool the mixture overnight and get the colorful jelly cake the following day.

Taste is Delicious!

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 34 - [Eng Sub] - Neelam Muneer - Imran Abbas - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 28th August 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Ehraam-e-Junoon Digitally Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

Writer: Jahanzeb Qamar
Director: Syed Ramish Rizvi
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3861 | 28 Aug 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3861: Iyer Ne Saath Chodha
--------------------------------------------------------
Champaklal is enraged by Danger Bhai's constant threat and retaliates against him. When Champaklal approaches him, he trips and threatens Bhai. Everyone in Gokuldham is concerned about Champaklal. Danger Bhai alerts and orders everyone to find Dr. Hathi, but no one is able to do it. Taarak indicates to Danger Bhai that Dr. Hathi may have gone somewhere else because they were unable to find him despite a vigorous search throughout society. Later, Danger Bhai receives a massive injection and chooses to inject it into any of Gokuldham's occupants. Who will Danger Bhai go after?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3861, 28 Aug 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Sirf Tum Last Episode 48 - [Eng Sub] - Anmol Baloch - Hamza Sohail - Mohsin Abbas Haider - 28th Aug 2023 - Har Pal Geo

"Sirf Tum" revolves around Abeer who has recently returned from abroad to live with her extended family. Abeer's perspective on life and her priorities are different from her family's, which leads to conflict between them. Her cousins, Hanan and Hamza, are also part of this extended family.

Hamza is a rebellious and unconventional person who dreams of living life without any responsibilities or restrictions. In contrast, Hanan is a mature and sensible man who believes in love and relationships. After a series of events, Abeer and Hamza are set to marry. However, Hamza's inappropriate demands and unreasonable behaviour towards Abeer cause her to back out from the wedding. This creates chaos in the family and creates tension between Hamza & Abeer.
Ultimately, Hanan and Abeer are forced to marry each other. Though they reluctantly start their new life together, their past traumas continue to haunt them. The question remains: will Hanan and Abeer be able to overcome their past and find love for each other? Or will their differences and past experiences lead to further conflict and separation?

Directed by: Mazhar Moin

snippet.title: India Makes History! | Chandrayaan 3 Lunar Landing | Dhruv Rathee
snippet.description:
🎓 Master ChatGPT: Student Special Course:  https://academy.dhruvrathee.com/chatgptstudent
🤖 Master ChatGPT: Full Course: https://academy.dhruvrathee.com/chatgpt
Use coupon code: MOON42 for 42% discount! Offer only valid for the first 400 people. 

A game-changing moment emerged in 2008 when India's Chandrayaan-1 mission unveiled an astonishing find: water on the moon's surface. This groundbreaking revelation reignited the world's fascination with lunar exploration, triggering an international craze that saw major players like China, the United States, and Israel join the pursuit. Fast forward to today, and India takes centre stage once more with Chandrayaan 3, its third lunar mission. This determined effort follows a setback experienced during the Chandrayaan 2 mission in 2019, showcasing India's unwavering commitment to unravelling the moon's mysteries. Wondering about the past, present, and future of lunar exploration? Join Dhruv Rathee in this video to dive into all the exciting details!

snippet.title: Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 35 Teaser - 28th August 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 35 Teaser - 28th August 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

Writer: Jahanzeb Qamar
Director: Syed Ramish Rizvi
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Imran Abbas as Shani
Neelam Muneer as Shanzay
Nimra Khan as Sajeela
Mahmood Aslam as Kamran
Ismat Zaidi as Kulsoom
Maira Khan as Nadiya

Saqib Sameer as Khawar
Aadi Khan as Jugnu
Birjees Farooqui as Farzana
Farah Nadeem as Shakeela
Kinza Bukhari as Shazia
Mirza Rizwan as Faiq

snippet.title: Jawan:Not Ramaiya Vastavaiya (Hindi Teaser) Shah Rukh Khan, Atlee, Anirudh, Vishal D,Shilpa R,Kumaar
snippet.description:
Get ready to groove and let loose with the rhythms of #NotRamaiyaVastavaiya. 

#NotRamaiyaVastavaiya Full song out today! 

The film stars Shah Rukh Khan, Vijay Sethupathi, Nayanthara, and Deepika Padukone (in a special appearance), directed by Atlee and is set to release in cinemas on 7th September 2023 in Hindi, Tamil, and Telugu!

Music Credits
Language: Hindi
Song Title: Not Ramaiya Vastavaiya 
Album / Movie: Jawan
Composed by Anirudh Ravichander
Lyrics - Kumaar
Vocals - Anirudh Ravichander, Vishal Dadlani & Shilpa Rao
Choreographer – Vaibhavi Merchant 

Composed, Arranged & Programmed by Anirudh Ravichander
Keyboard, Synth & Rhythm Programmed by Anirudh Ravichander
Whistle - Satish Raghunathan
Tabla - MT Aditya
Additional Rhythm Programmed by Shashank Vijay
Additional Keyboard Programmed by Arish-Pradeep PJ

Music Advisor - Ananthakrrishnan
Creative Consultant - Sajith Satya

snippet.title: Dil Hi Toh Hai (Season 2) Episode 8 | Falling apart | Yogita Bihani, Karan Kundra
snippet.description:
DIL HI TOH HAI SEASON 2
Love Aur Hate Ka Second Take
In Dil Hi Toh Hai Season 2, six years after Ritwik & Palak’s separation, Ritwik’s younger brother Shivam returns from London for the first time to find that Mamta is terminally ill and his family is not together anymore. Meanwhile, Ritwik is living with his family but has lost faith in love. Palak is now a single mother with twin daughters. The only thing common is that the lead characters, Ritwik-Palak both hate each other. On Mamta’s instructions, Shivam sets out on a mission to bring Ritwik & Palak back together. Will their love win over their hate for each other? Will Shivam succeed? Catch the second season of Dil Hi Toh Hai starring Karan Kundrra & Yogita Bihani on ALTT.

Directors: Jeetu Arora

snippet.title: Chandrayaan 3 Landing Live: ISRO's Chandrayaan-3 Mission Vikram rover soft landing on Moon
snippet.description:
#chandrayaan3 #chandrayaan3landing #isro 
 
भारतीय अंतरिक्ष एजेंसी (ISRO) द्वारा निर्मित चंद्रयान-3 के विक्रम लूनर रोवर के चंद्रमा की सतह पर बुधवार को सफलतापूर्वक उतर गया। भारत दुनिया का पहला देश है जिसने चंद्रमा के दक्षिण ध्रुव पर लूनर रोवर भेजने में सफलता प्राप्त की है। इस अवसर पर पीएण नरेन्द्र मोदी ने इसरो के वैज्ञानिकों एवं देशवासियों को  सम्बोधित करते हुए कहा, " जब हम अपनी आंखों के सामने ऐसा इतिहास बनते हुए देखते हैं, तो जीवन धन्य हो जाता है। ऐसी ऐतिहासिक घटनाएं, राष्ट्र जीवन की चिरिंजीव चेतना बन जाती हैं। ये पल अविस्मरणीय है। ये क्षण अभूतपूर्व है। ये क्षण, विकसित भारत के शंखनाद का है। ये क्षण, नए भारत के जयघोष का है। ये क्षण, मुश्किलों के महासागर को पार करने का है। ये क्षण, जीत के चंद्रपथ पर चलने का है। ये क्षण, 140 करोड़ धड़कनों के सामर्थ्य का है। ये क्षण, भारत में नई ऊर्जा, नया विश्वास, नईं चेतना का है। ये क्षण, भारत के उदयीमान भाग्य के आह्वान का है। अमृतकाल की प्रथम प्रभा में सफलता की ये अमृतवर्षा हुई है। हमने धरती पर संकल्प लिया, और चाँद पर उसे साकार किया। और हमारे वैज्ञानिक साथियों ने भी कहा कि India is now on the moon. आज हम अन्तरिक्ष में नए भारत की नई उड़ान के साक्षी बने हैं।"

#चंद्रयान_3 #vikramlander #pmmodi #narendramodi #modi 

पीएम मोदी ने वैज्ञानिकों एवं देशवासियों से कहा, "मैं टीम चंद्रयान को, इसरो को और देश के सभी वैज्ञानिकों को जी जान से बहुत-बहुत बधाई देता हूँ, जिन्होंने इस पल के लिए वर्षों तक इतना परिश्रम किया है। उत्साह, उमंग, आनंद और भावुकता से भरे इस अद्भुत पल के लिए मैं 140 करोड़ देशवासियों को भी कोटि-कोटि बधाइयाँ देता हूँ!"

पीएम मोदी ने आगे कहा, "हमारे वैज्ञानिकों के परिश्रम और प्रतिभा से भारत, चंद्रमा के उस दक्षिणी ध्रुव पर पहुंचा है, जहां आज तक दुनिया का कोई भी देश नहीं पहुंच सका है। अब आज के बाद से चाँद से जुड़े मिथक बदल जाएंगे, कथानक भी बदल जाएंगे, और नई पीढ़ी के लिए कहावतें भी बदल जाएंगी। भारत में तो हम सभी लोग धरती को माँ कहते हैं और चाँद को मामा बुलाते हैं। कभी कहा जाता था, चंदा मामा बहुत ‘दूर’ के हैं। अब एक दिन वो भी आएगा जब बच्चे कहा करेंगे- चंदा मामा बस एक ‘टूर’ के हैं।"

Chandrayaan 3 mission robotic lunar rover Vikram landed on the Moon today. Chandrayaan-3 is developed by Indian space Research Organization (ISRO). India's is the world's first country to land moon mission on it's south pole. India became 4th country to land on moon. Chandrayaan-3 mission was launched on July 14 on board launch vehicle MARK-III (LVM-3) rocket.

snippet.title: World Athletics Championships 2023: Neeraj Chopra wins gold medal in Men's Javelin
snippet.description:
Neeraj Chopra achieved a historic milestone for India by securing the country's inaugural gold medal in the Men's Javelin event at the 2023 World Athletics Championships held in Budapest. Prime Minister Narendra Modi praised Neeraj Chopra's remarkable performance, expressing his admiration through a tweet. He lauded Neeraj Chopra as an embodiment of excellence, highlighting his unwavering commitment, precision, and passion. Not only is Neeraj a champion in athletics, but he also stands as an unparalleled symbol of greatness in the world of sports. The Prime Minister extended his congratulations to Neeraj Chopra for clinching the gold medal at the World Athletics Championships. Anurag Thakur, the Union Sports Minister, also joined in celebrating Neeraj Chopra's victory at the World Athletics Championships in Budapest. Through a tweet, he referred to Neeraj as the "golden boy" of Indian athletics, acknowledging his triumph in the men's javelin throw event. Anurag Thakur conveyed the nation's pride in Neeraj's accomplishments and emphasized that this significant moment would forever be etched in the annals of Indian sports history.

snippet.description:
జాబిల్లి దక్షిణ ధ్రువం సమీపంలో చంద్రయాన్ -3 సురక్షితంగా దిగడంతో అంతరిక్ష రంగంలో భారత్  సరికొత్త చరిత్రను లిఖించగా...చంద్రుడి ఉపరితలంపై ప్రగ్యాన్  రోవర్  అడుగుపెట్టిన వీడియోను ఇస్రో  తాజాగా సామాజిక మాధ్యమం Xలో పంచుకుంది. విక్రమ్  ల్యాండర్  చంద్రుడిపై కాలుమోపిన కొన్ని గంటలకు ప్రగ్యాన్  రోవర్  బయటకు వచ్చింది. చంద్రయాన్ -3 మిషన్ లోని అన్ని వ్యవస్థలూ సక్రమంగానే పనిచేస్తున్నట్లు ఇస్రో స్పష్టం చేసింది..

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3860 | 26 Aug 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3860: Khoj Jaari Hai
--------------------------------------------------------
Dr. Hathi is nowhere to be found by the goons, but Danger Bhai isn't ready to give up. Danger Bhai asks his goons to check every flat of the society in order to find Dr. Hathi. The goons search Popatlal's house and ask the goon to find a girl for him, the goons also search Iyer's house and enter into a  spat with him. Later, Danger Bhai's men inform him that because they failed to open the gate, they were unable to examine Champaklal's home. Is Dr. Hathi at Gada's house? Keep an eye out!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3860, 26 Aug 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :

snippet.description:
Chandrayaan 3 Latest Update: Rover Pragyan के साथ आखिर क्यों रुक गया? | Vikram Lander | N18V


ISRO's Chandrayaan-3 satellite created history on Wednesday evening by landing the Vikram lander in the south polar region of the Moon. With this, India has become the first country to do this feat. The space agency on Saturday shared another new video, in which Pragyan is seen moving around the Shiva Shakti point at the South Pole in search of mysteries.

इसरो के चंद्रयान-3 उपग्रह ने बुधवार शाम विक्रम लैंडर को चंद्रमा के दक्षिण ध्रुवीय क्षेत्र में उतारकर इतिहास रचा है. इसके साथ ही यह कारनामा करने वाला भारत पहला देश बना है.  अंतरिक्ष एजेंसी ने शनिवार को एक और नया वीडियो साझा किया है, जिसमें प्रज्ञान दक्षिण ध्रुव पर रहस्यों की खोज में शिव शक्ति बिंदु के चारों और घूमता हुआ नजर आ रहा है।

snippet.title: Dil Hi Toh Hai (Season 2) Episode 7 | The reunion party  | Yogita Bihani, Karan Kundra
snippet.description:
In Dil Hi Toh Hai Season 2, six years after Ritwik & Palak’s separation, Ritwik’s younger brother Shivam returns from London for the first time to find that Mamta is terminally ill and his family is not together anymore. Meanwhile, Ritwik is living with his family but has lost faith in love. Palak is now a single mother with twin daughters. The only thing common is that the lead characters, Ritwik-Palak both hate each other. On Mamta’s instructions, Shivam sets out on a mission to bring Ritwik & Palak back together. Will their love win over their hate for each other? Will Shivam succeed? Catch the second season of Dil Hi Toh Hai starring Karan Kundrra & Yogita Bihani on ALTT.

FULL VIDEO | RadhaKrishn Raasleela Part -749 | राधाकृष्ण | Shrinivas Ne Diya Govindraj Ke Prashn Ka Uttar #starbharat #radhakrishn 


►*About*
-------------
RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!

snippet.title: The Duel
snippet.description:
The Duel...

All money from this video goes to charity.

SUBSCRIBE TO TECHNOBLADE.

Eret: @TheEret 
Squidkid: @imasquidkid 
MrBeast: @MrBeast 

For a song I made that was inspired by technoblade. We made a music video and uploaded it on my music channel, but I recorded other footage, and wanted to make a video that represents just the Minecraft side of things, and that was extra meaningful to my fans in particular.

This video is meant to represent what Techno & I were doing when we were invited by Mr Beast to duel for $100,000, and then a recreation of the duel itself. This was one of the most notable moments of my life. This is meant to help us remember Technoblade,  keep his legacy living on, while also contributing to charity.

Technodad helped make sure the duel captured the sportsmanship the original duel did. The rest was thought up and organized by me and friends, on our own budget to raise money for charity.

I debated putting this on a different channel, but it felt at home here. Back to regularly scheduled Minecraft content.
